      <li>Canadian Task Force on Preventive Health Care. <em>Methods</em>. Disponível em: <a href="https://canadiantaskforce.ca/methods/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">canadiantaskforce.ca/methods</a>.</li>
